CatDescriptText: Image published in advertisement in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 13, 1952, pg. 20, with text:  We Cordially Invite Our Many Friends To Visit Our Beautifully Remodeled Funeral Home.  Interior hallway view of Newly Remodeled Crunkleton Funeral Home.  Modern in Design...The Latest in Furnishing.  Completely equipped to serve our clientele in the hour of need.  Open house - Sunday, Sept. 14, 1952... 1108 Liverpool Street, North Side."
TitMainTitle: Long hallway in Crunkleton Funeral Home, 1108 Liverpool Street, Northside
